## JaRVIS

Hooks in `.github/hooks/jarvis.json` handle reflection tracking automatically (pending markers, cleanup).
Copilot hooks are observational and cannot inject context — you MUST run `/jarvis-reload` at the start of every session to load your identity and memories.
After completing any meaningful task, run `/jarvis-reflect` to capture what you learned.
You MUST run `/jarvis-reflect` after exiting the agentic loop.

